Mbali Khanyile Kuthiwa abasolwa abane ababanjwe ngoLwesihlanu baneminyaka ephakathi kuka-16 no-25, babhadanywe kwenye indlu okuqashe kuyo omunye wabo lapho bekufihlwe khona ezinye izimpahla okuthiwa zantshontshwa. Omunye okhale ngokuntshontshelwa izimpahla zasendlini ngesonto eledlule, uMnuz Mfekazi ukhale ngobugebengu obudlangile eMfekayi, uthe iyamkhathaza indlela ubugebengu obudlange ngayo. “Basimoshe kakhulu abasigqekezela ngoba kuningi abakuthatha endlini. Bangena bantshotsha izimpahla zasekhishini, badlulela emagunjini okulala bazenzele nje. Ngaleso sikhathi, mina ngangilele endlini engaphandle ngingaboni ukuthi kuyonakala,” kusho uMfekazi. Phakathi kwezimpahla okuthiwa zitholwe emqashweni womunye wabasolwa kubalwa imisakazo, izimpahla zokugqoka nethelevishini. Ezinye zazo kubikwa ukuthi zitholwe zigqitshiwe. Ikhansela laku-ward 11 kule ndawo, uMnuz Zakhele Nyawo lithe emva kokuthi kube nezigameko zokugqekezelwa kwabantu, nemibiko engapheli yokuntshontshelwa, bahlele nekomiti ukuthi baqhube umkhankaso wokulwa nobugebengu ngokubambisana namaphoyisa. “Umphakathi uthole umkhondo wabasolwa okuthiwa bebengena bazenzele emizini yabantu begqekeza. Sibe sesihlangana ngenhloso yokulwa nalo mkhuba,” kubeka uNyawo. Uthe yize engahambisani nokushaywa kwabantu abasolwa ebugebengwini kodwa ngalo mkhankaso uyafisa ukuthi bunqandeke ubugebengu. Esikuzwile wukuthi lezi zingane (abasolwa) zinabantu ezisebenzisana nabo endaweni nesikholwa ukuthi bayogcina bebanjiwe nabo,” kuchaza ikhansela. Amaphoyisa kuthiwa atshele ababefuna ukuvula amacala ukuthi amakhompuyuthwa awasebenzi. Amacala okwebelwa kwamalungu omphakathi angavulwa.